{"tid":1474662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李一平 : 中共將殺害港警嫁禍反送中","createTime":"2019-08-15T09:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T16:24:55.000Z","uid":266547,"like":64,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"d980f3ab9a6e602eae39375193e12af2cecfc1e6","tid":1474662,"uid":266547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:08:47.000Z","msg":"李一平係中國異議人士、加拿大華人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pOQBpY2rbx4&amp;t=636s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpOQBpY2rbx4%26t%3D636s&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdkyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=01d7222b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pOQBpY2rbx4&amp;t=636s</a><br />\n李一平 : <br />\n我從體制內得到的消息是，為了鎮壓這次反送終運動，中共已做了三項安排<br />\n第一，中共已派遣了數千名防暴警察進入香港。<br />\n第二，中共已派出幾百個便衣特務，混進香港的抗爭隊伍中，冒充勇武派年輕人，要在8月18號襲擊香港警察。他們已經計劃好要殺死幾個香港警察，然後嫁禍給勇武派年青人。<br />\n第三，深圳已集結了幾萬名武警，一旦特務殺害了香港警察，而香港警方不願意或者沒能夠全面鎮壓街頭的勇武派(便衣特務?)之後，林鄭月娥就會宣布，說暴亂失控，然後就會公開要求中共派兵平亂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望係流料<br />\n經過左811血腥鎮壓，我地已經得到好多國際支持，呢個時候一定唔可以發生殺死警察呢啲野。"},{"pid":"2d33f29eafed109c75f6f4fb542a5b55973593f6","tid":1474662,"uid":194298,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:09:42.000Z","msg":"ON9"},{"pid":"50c655bda259451c667161426cedb5a1d8c6bde3","tid":1474662,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5664fbb52df58b4e56e1a95d2f9ccebcc0c8977b","tid":1474662,"uid":53003,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:10:51.000Z","msg":"警察人人自危<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f86186ce7ea6021c820d1b163ff9e911288ea11","tid":1474662,"uid":84303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},